     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Rdng hppns t b n f my fvrt thngs n th wrld. I knw, I’m nt ln —  fw thrs sm t njy t s wll. Bt th rdr ths dys fcs ntrstng chllngs: thr’s mr t rd thn vr, n s mny dffrnt frms, cmng t y vry dy, nd  mlln dstrctns frm th ct f rdng (mny f thm n th frm f thr rdng).
      </p>
      <p>
       Th typs f rdng sm t grw ll th tm: frm trdtnl ppr bks, nwspprs nd mgzns t blg psts, nln nws rtcls, frms, Twts, Fcbk pdts, mls, ml nwslttrs, nd mch mr. Ech f ths typs f rdng prsnts n vr-grwng nd ftn vrwhlmng rdng lst tht w mst kp p wth: n ml nbx, n
       <span class="caps">
        RSS
       </span>
       rdr wth th ltst blg psts, vrs nws wbsts,  lng lst f stts pdts nd frm psts, nd s n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Kpng p wth ths lsts bcms nr mpssbl,  fll-tm jb. My sltn s t gv p n kpng p — t’s  slf-nvntd nd, nt  rl n — nd t pr dwn s mch s pssbl. S I pr my lst f blgs t th ssntl, I brly d ml, I hv nly  fw frnds n Twttr nd Fcbk. S I’m nt th mst p-t-dt gy, nd s I dn’t mk vryn hppy by bng thr nln frnd … lf sms t g n.
      </p>
      <p>
       Evn wth  prd-dwn rdng lst, rdng cn stll b  chllng: hw d y rd wtht dstrctns? It’s ncrdbly dffclt, s ch rdng frm plls s wy frm th thrs, nd lrts nd pdts r cmng n ll th tm, nt t mntn thr frms f cmmnctn lk phns,
       <span class="caps">
        IM,
       </span>
       nd (gsp) rl ppl tryng t gt r ttntn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hr’s hw I fnd ndstrctd rdng:
      </p>
      <p>
       1.
       <strong>
        Bks
       </strong>
       . My fvrt typ f rdng s th nvl. I rrly rd nn-fctn bks, vn thgh I’m  nn-fctn thr myslf. And whl th Pd nd Kndl ch prsnt lvly wys f rdng bks, thy ls ch cntn vrs dstrctns. And s I stll lv th ppr bk, fr ts smplcty nd lck f thr thngs t d whl y’r rdng t. Cls th cmptr, trn ff th phns, fnd  qt spt, nd jst rd. Try t d t n lrg chnks, lk 30 mnts r n hr r mr, nd y cn gt lst n nthr wrld. Smply btfl.
      </p>
      <p>
       2.
       <strong>
        Blg psts
       </strong>
       . I lv t rd blgs, thgh I kp p wth fwr ths dys thn I dd  fw yrs g. I’v prd my rdng lst dwn nd s Ggl Rdr t qckly gt thrgh th lst ch dy. Whn I fnd  pst I wnt t rd n fll, wtht dstrctns, I pn t n  nw brwsr wndw — nt  brwsr tb, bt  wndw, s n thr tbs shw — nd s th
       <a href="http://lab.arc90.com/experiments/readability/">
        Rdblty bkmrklt
       </a>
       r smlr t fcs nly n th txt. Thn I rd wtht swtchng t nythng ls ntl I’m dn.
      </p>
      <p>
       Hr n mnmlst, nd thr n
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net">
        Zn Hbts
       </a>
       , I’v lrdy prd my psts dwn t jst th txt. I’v dn th wrk fr y, fr ndstrctd rdng. On thr blgs, y hv t d sm wrk — nstll th Rdblty bkmrklt, ht  bttn whn y wnt t rd n rtcl wtht dstrctns. It’s
       <span class="caps">
        OK.
       </span>
       A lttl hrd wrk nvr klld nyn, xcpt my Uncl Mrry bt I thnk t ws mr hs cmplnng bt hrd wrk tht dd t.
      </p>
      <p>
       3.
       <strong>
        Fcsd brwsng
       </strong>
       . If y pn  bnch f tbs, kp thngs fcsd by sng  lttl srvc I dscvrd clld
       <a href="http://www.instapaper.com/">
        Instppr
       </a>
       (I dn’t thnk nyn ls knws bt ths, s fl fr t lv 5 cnts n yr wy t fr th tp). Instppr ll yr pn tbs fr rdng ltr, thn rd n t  tm whn y hv sm ndstrctd rdng tm.
      </p>
      <p>
       4.
       <strong>
        Eml, Twttr, Fcbk
       </strong>
       . Bsclly, pn ths s lttl s pssbl. Thy ld t dstrctns fr thr rdng, fr wrk, tc. Opn thm fr 5 mnts, d  qck scn, pst n pdt r rply f ncssry, thn gt t. Only pn n t  tm, d thm wth fcs, nd cls th tb. Gv yrslf sm tm t d ths n  rglr bss — 5 mnts t th tp f ch hr, r t 9 .m. nd 3 p.m., r whtvr wrks fr y.
      </p>
      <p>
       5.
       <strong>
        Nws rtcls
       </strong>
       . I dn’t rd  lt f nws sts. Thy tnd t ld t lts f dstrctns. Bt whn I d, I pn  fw f th rtcls tht lk ntrstng, scn thm, nd Instppr th ns tht I wnt t rd ltr. Thn I’ll plw thrgh Instppr wth sm ndstrctd rdng, whn I hv tm.
